data.description: Come and tour this beautiful 4 bedroom/3 full bath home in Ardmore Reserve today! This 2021 home is in LIKE NEW condition and has been very well maintained. Nestled amidst the tranquil landscapes of Minneola, Florida, this inviting residence offers a harmonious blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior that exudes warmth and character. The great room is bathed in natural light, creating an inviting ambiance throughout. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the bedrooms, great room, and chef’s kitchen, fostering a sense of togetherness for both daily living and entertaining. The open-concept upgraded kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a gas stove, ample storage, and solid stone countertops. Retreat to the oversized bedrooms, including a master suite that offers an oversized shower and separate garden tub, ensuring a comfortable and private haven for relaxation. Step outside to discover your very own outdoor oasis with no rear neighbors. Relax on the architectural patio, where you can savor your morning coffee or host gatherings with friends and family, all while soaking in the picturesque views of the surrounding countryside. The patio is equipped with a gas line and is ready for you to install a summer kitchen.  Conveniently located in Minneola, this property provides a unique opportunity to enjoy the serenity of rural living without sacrificing convenience. Nearby, you'll find access to top-rated schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes, ensuring that you have access to everything you need. Don't miss the chance to make this charming retreat your own. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and explore the endless possibilities this property has to offer!
